ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with 2391766 Ontario Inc. (Forest Valley Terrace) ** NCC **
PrecisOrder Approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant three extension options of ten years each, beginning on May 1, 2033, May 1, 2043, and May 1, 2053, to extend an existing lease with 2391766 ONTARIO INC., operating as Forest Valley Terrace, to occupy the premises at 1510 ST. JOSEPH BOULEVARD, in Ottawa.
